This is a placeholder for the generated Android APK. 
To build the real binary APK using your Progressive Web App, run the following commands on your local machine:

1. Install Node.js (if not installed)
2. Open terminal and run: npm install -g @bubblewrap/cli
3. cd into this folder (SSC-AI-Dashboard)
4. Run: bubblewrap init --manifest=http://localhost:8000/manifest.json
5. Run: bubblewrap build

This will compile the real 'app-release-signed.apk' using the Android SDK.